img%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20open%20kitchen%20at%20Micasadeco%20%26amp%3B%20Cafe%20in%20Tokyo.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684c66f4f748d8c055f3af28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20open%20kitchen%20at%20Micasadeco%20%26amp%3B%20Cafe%20in%20Tokyo.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chefs%20expertly%20mixed%20and%20flipped%20their%20pancake%20batter%20as%20a%20row%20of%20orders%20waited%20on%20the%20counter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20jaws%20dropped%20as%20the%20first%20plate%20of%20pancakes%20arrived.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Original%20souffle%20pancakes%20from%20Micasadeco%26amp%3BCafe%20in%20Tokyo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683fb5a5c19ab3675c109809%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20plate%20of%20ricotta%20cheese%20pancakes.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20ricotta%20cheese%20pancakes%20are%20the%20most%20popular%20order%20at%20Micasadeco%20%26amp%3B%20Cafe.%20The%20dish%2C%20which%20cost%201%2C750%20yen%2C%20or%20about%20%2412%2C%20featured%20three%20plump%20pancakes%20with%20a%20side%20of%20cream%2C%20plus%20maple%20syrup%20served%20in%20a%20mini%20beaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20dish%20arrived%20with%20%26quot%3BMerci%26quot%3B%20spelled%20out%20in%20powdered%20sugar%2C%20a%20sweet%20thank%20you%20from%20the%20chef.%20The%20pancakes%2C%20topped%20with%20a%20perfectly%20square%20butter%20knob%2C%20looked%20so%20plump%20you%20could%20rest%20your%20head%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20boyfriend%20and%20I%20couldn't%20resist%20moving%20the%20plate%20around%2C%20laughing%20like%20kids%20as%20we%20watched%20the%20pancakes%20jiggle.%20Micasadeco%20%26amp%3B%20Cafe%20says%20on%20its%20website%20that%20souffl%C3%A9%20pancakes%20are%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bdancing%20pancakes.%26quot%3B%20I%20couldn't%20think%20of%20a%20more%20fitting%20nickname.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20souffl%C3%A9%20pancakes%20were%20as%20delicious%20and%20fluffy%20as%20they%20looked.%20Their%20texture%20was%20light%20as%20air%2C%20melting%20in%20my%20mouth%2C%20and%20the%20ricotta%20cheese%20and%20fresh%20cream%20added%20a%20lovely%20hint%20of%20sweetness.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20boyfriend%20and%20I%20were%20also%20huge%20fans%20of%20the%20maple%20syrup.%20I%20was%20shocked%20to%20learn%20it%20was%20from%20Costco's%20Kirkland%20brand%2C%20a%20discovery%20I%20made%20when%20I%20spotted%20the%20bottle%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20bathroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20also%20tried%20the%20seasonal%20sakura%20pancakes%2C%20which%20looked%20stunning%20on%20the%20plate.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sakura%20pancakes%20from%20Micasadeco%26amp%3BCafe%20in%20Tokyo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683fb5749b2a601d01b241a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20plate%20of%20the%20seasonal%20sakura%20pancakes.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pancakes%2C%20which%20cost%201%2C950%20yen%2C%20or%20about%20%2414%2C%20were%20infused%20with%20sakura%20powder%20and%20topped%20with%20matcha%20and%20strawberry%20cream%2C%20as%20well%20as%20fresh%20strawberries.%20Matcha%20syrup%20and%20fresh%20strawberry-infused%20cream%20were%20also%20provided%20on%20the%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20texture%20was%20just%20as%20light%20and%20cloud-like%20as%20the%20ricotta%20cheese%20pancakes%2C%20but%20tinged%20with%20that%20subtle%20sakura%20flavor.%20The%20pancakes%20tasted%20surprising%20and%20sweet%2C%20pairing%20perfectly%20with%20the%20fresh%20strawberry%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20the%20flavor%20of%20the%20pancakes%20so%20much%20that%20I%20didn't%20even%20use%20the%20matcha%20or%20maple%20syrups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20loved%20trying%20Japan's%20famous%20souffl%C3%A9%20pancakes%20in%20Harajuku.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anneta%20in%20Harajuku%2C%20Tokyo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683fb5dc9b2a601d01b241af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20also%20tried%20the%20famous%20tornado%20potato%20while%20I%20was%20in%20Harajuku.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMicasadeco%20%26amp%3B%20Cafe%20promises%20to%20deliver%20food%20that's%20%26quot%3BDelicious!%20Cute!%20Fun!%26quot%3B%20and%20its%20souffl%C3%A9%20pancakes%20were%20all%20of%20the%20above.%20They%20were%20delightful%20and%20playful%2C%20but%20also%20super%20delicious.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20dish%20that%20just%20looks%20good%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20lunch%20was%20a%20good%20reminder%20that%20sometimes%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftokyo-japan-teamlab-planets-museum-review-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etourist%20trap%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20can%20still%20be%20worth%20trying.%20It's%20a%20lesson%20we%20embraced%20as%20we%20walked%20through%20Takeshita%20Street%20and%20tried%20glazed%20strawberries%20on%20skewers%20and%20tornado%20potatoes%20%E2%80%94%20both%20delicious!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20if%20you're%20heading%20to%20Japan%2C%20seek%20out%20the%20hidden%20gems%2C%20but%20don't%20be%20afraid%20to%20try%20a%20few%20of%20the%20TikTok%20spots.%20Sometimes%20waiting%20in%20line%20is%20worth%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftokyo-japan-souffle-pancakes-review-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749