80%94%20between%20March%2025%20and%20April%2025%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20The%20platform%20compared%20prices%20between%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobotaxis-driverless-taxi-hurt-uber-lyft-drivers-waymo-tesla-zoox-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20Waymo%2C%20UberX%2C%20and%20Lyft%20Standard%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20found%20that%20the%20average%20price%20of%20a%20Waymo%20ride%20is%20%2420.43%2C%20which%20is%20%245.99%20more%20than%20an%20average%20Lyft%20ride%20and%20%244.85%20more%20than%20an%20average%20Uber%20ride.%20The%20average%20price%20of%20a%20Lyft%20was%20%2414.44%2C%20while%20the%20average%20price%20of%20an%20Uber%20was%20%2415.58.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWaymo%20rides%20cost%2041%25%20more%20than%20Lyft%20and%2031%25%20more%20than%20Uber%20on%20average%20when%20comparing%20pricing%20at%20the%20same%20time%20and%20across%20the%20same%20routes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20study%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20also%20looked%20at%20price%20differences%20during%20peak%20hours.%20It%20found%20that%20during%20the%20evening%20rush%20hour%20between%205%20p.m.%20and%206%20p.m.%2C%20a%20Waymo%20was%20about%20%2411%20more%20expensive%20than%20Lyft%20and%20nearly%20%249.50%20more%20for%20an%20Uber.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20Waymo%20is%20more%20expensive%20than%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20is%20consistent%20throughout%20the%20entire%20day%2C%20with%20the%20smallest%20price%20gap%20occurring%20at%20around%205%20a.m.%2C%20the%20study%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20some%20people%20appear%20to%20be%20willing%20to%20bite%20the%20extra%20couple%20of%20bucks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObi%20also%20distributed%20a%20consumer%20sentiment%20survey%20about%20Waymo%20to%20about%20500%20people%2C%20focusing%20on%20California%20and%20Phoenix%2C%20where%20robotaxis%20are%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20majority%20of%20respondents%20%E2%80%94%20about%2070%25%20%E2%80%94%20said%20they%20prefer%20%26quot%3Bthe%20experience%20of%20Waymo%20vs%20a%20regular%20rideshare%20with%20a%20driver%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20costs%20become%20a%20factor%2C%2042.7%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they'd%20be%20willing%20to%20pay%20more%2C%20but%20it%20would%20depend%20on%20how%20much%20more%20it%20would%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%2016.3%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they'd%20pay%20up%20to%20%2410%20more%2C%20while%2010.1%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they'd%20pay%20up%20to%20%245.%20Another%2016.3%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20would%20only%20pay%20less%20than%20%245.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%2039.1%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20would%20only%20pay%20the%20same%20or%20less%20for%20a%20Waymo%20and%2026.8%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20wouldn't%20take%20one%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20study%20doesn't%20factor%20in%20tipping%20to%20the%20final%20cost%20of%20an%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%2C%2026%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20that%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-self-driving-robotaxi-cars-without-drivers-amazing-tech-review-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprefer%20Waymo%20because%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20leave%20a%20tip%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Waymo%20fans%20who%20have%20previously%20spoken%20to%20Business%20Insider%20point%20to%20this%20flexibility%20and%20the%20overall%20experience%20of%20having%20a%20car%20to%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWaymo%20is%20simply%20a%20better%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-uber-angel-investor-kevin-hartz-vc-a-star-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKevin%20Hartz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20VC%20and%20early%20Uber%20angel%20investor%2C%20told%20BI%20back%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20published%20by%20the%20California%20Public%20Utilities%20Commission%20showed%20that%20the%20take-up%20by%20riders%20has%20quickly%20grown%20in%20the%20few%20years%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A