-fueled%20performances%20with%20male%20sex%20workers%20%E2%80%94%20Ventura%20called%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsean-diddy-combs-indictment-allegations-freak-off-sex-performances-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bfreak%20offs%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Jane%2C%20a%20pseudonym%2C%20called%20them%20%26quot%3Bhotel%20nights%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20have%20also%20presented%20strong%20evidence%20that%20force%2C%20fraud%2C%20and%20coercion%20were%20all%20in%20play%20in%20these%20two%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20women%20have%20described%20vicious%20beatings%20at%20Combs'%20hands%2C%20accounts%20strengthened%20by%20photographs%20of%20their%20bruises%20and%20eyewitness%20corroboration.%20Jurors%20have%20also%20seen%20years%20of%20emails%20and%20text%20messages%20in%20which%20the%20women%20tell%20Combs%20of%20their%20anguish%20over%20his%20violence%20and%20broken%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20federal%20law%20requires%20sex%20trafficking%20%3Cem%3Ethrough%3C%2Fem%3E%20force%2C%20fraud%2C%20or%20coercion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20must%20show%20that%20these%20were%20linked.%20And%20if%20at%20least%20one%20juror%20questions%20this%20link%20%E2%80%94%20if%20they%20find%20that%20Ventura%20and%20Jane%20engaged%20in%20years%20of%20freak%20offs%20or%20hotel%20nights%20willingly%2C%20and%20not%20because%20Combs%20made%20them%20%E2%80%94%20then%20the%20trial%20could%20end%20in%20a%20mistrial%20or%20acquittal%20on%20the%20sex-trafficking%20counts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20the%20defense%20has%20worked%20so%20hard%20to%20blur%20the%20link%20between%20freak%20offs%2C%20or%20hotel%20nights%2C%20and%20the%20violence%20and%20betrayal%20that%20also%20permeated%20these%20relationships%2C%20the%20former%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20trying%20to%20show%20Combs%20had%20sexual%20desires%20and%20sexual%20interests%20and%20sexual%20curiosities%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bachner%2C%20who%20was%20on%20the%20defense%20team%20when%20Combs%20was%20acquitted%20of%20gun%20possession%20and%20bribery%20in%20state%20court%20in%20Manhattan%20in%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20women%20were%20more%20than%20willing%20to%20fulfill%20those%20desires%20and%20those%20inquiries%2C%20so%20long%20as%20they%20felt%20that%20they%20were%20being%20properly%20compensated%2C%26quot%3B%20both%20financially%20and%20emotionally%2C%20Bachner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20years%20that%20these%20freak%20offs%20and%20hotel%20nights%20were%20happening%20%E2%80%94%20between%202009%20and%202018%20for%20Ventura%2C%20and%20between%202021%20and%202024%20for%20Jane%20%E2%80%94%20both%20women%20exchanged%20explicit%20texts%20with%20Combs%20in%20which%20they%20professed%2C%20at%20times%2C%20to%20show%20their%20enjoyment%20of%20these%20sexual%20marathons%2C%20according%20to%20trial%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20sketch%20by%20a%20courtroom%20artist%20shows%20Cassie%20Ventura%20testifying%20at%20Sean%20%26quot%3BDiddy%26quot%3B%20Combs%20sex-trafficking%20and%20racketeering%20trial.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f48559b2a601d01b23a1a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECassie%20Ventura%20testified%20during%20the%20first%20week%20of%20Sean%20%26quot%3BDiddy%26quot%3B%20Combs%20sex-trafficking%20and%20racketeering%20trial.%3Cp%3EJane%20Rosenberg%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20texts%20show%20their%20apparent%20humiliation%20and%20regret%20over%20these%20marathons.%20On%20the%20witness%20stand%2C%20both%20women%20testified%20that%20they%20only%20pretended%20to%20enjoy%20themselves%20at%20the%20time%20due%20to%20Combs'%20violence%20and%20their%20emotional%20and%20financial%20dependence%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20both%20women%20s