n%20a%20totally%20different%20biome%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20spending%20three%20or%20four%20days%20driving%20across%20and%20seeing%20the%20gradual%20change%20is%20probably%20my%20favorite%20part.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2292ab7a9e-b322-4429-9c4f-27200f3d03bb%5C%22%3ECheaper%20gas%20and%20more%20driving%20this%20summer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20record%20numbers%20of%20Americans%20hit%20the%20road%20for%20the%20first%20big%20vacation%20weekend%20of%20the%20year%2C%20per%20AAA.%20It%20projected%20that%20over%201%20million%20more%20Americans%20would%20be%20traveling%20by%20car%20Memorial%20Day%20Weekend%20compared%20to%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%20an%20increase%20from%2038.2%20million%20auto%20travelers%20in%202024%20to%2039.4%20million%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20urge%20to%20stay%20domestic%20seems%20like%20it'll%20continue%20through%20the%20Fourth%20of%20July%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.airbnb.com%2Fstars-stripes-and-staycations-what-travelers-are-doing-this-july-4th%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAirbnb%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20bookings%20within%20300%20miles%20of%20vacationers'%20origin%20spots%20are%20up%2032%25%20over%20the%20Fourth%20of%20July%20weekend%20compared%20to%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnterprise%20Mobility%2C%20whose%20brands%20include%20Enterprise%20Rent-A-Car%2C%20National%20Car%20Rental%2C%20and%20Alamo%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20company%20is%20seeing%20a%20year-over-year%20increase%20in%20expected%20leisure%20travel%20from%20their%20non-airport%20locations%20in%20both%20June%20and%20July%20%E2%80%94%20what%20Enterprise%20deemed%20a%20signal%20of%20customers%20leaning%20into%20road%20trips%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20continuing%20to%20prioritize%20travel%2C%20and%20our%20research%20shows%20an%20increased%20interest%20in%20road%20trips%20this%20summer%2C%26quot%3B%20Bridget%20Long%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20North%20American%20operations%20at%20Enterprise%20Mobility%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20gas%20prices%20have%20come%20down%20from%202022-era%20highs%2C%20making%20it%20more%20affordable%20to%20hit%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FL5CoM%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ELillian%20Rafson%2C%20CEO%20of%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etravel%20agency%20Pack%20Up%20%2B%20Go%2C%20which%20plans%20US-based%20surprise%20vacations%20%E2%80%94%20where%20destinations%20are%20unknown%20and%20travelers%20give%20an%20overview%20of%20what%20they're%20interested%20in%20%E2%80%94%20said%20that%20the%20last%20few%20months%20have%20seen%20a%20surge%20of%20interest%20in%20road%20trip%20packages%2C%20compared%20to%20last%20year.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAlready%2C%2047%25%20of%20vacations%20booked%20through%20the%20agency%20in%20June%20were%20road%20trips%2C%20compared%20to%2027%25%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERafson%20said%20that%20during%20times%20of%20perceived%20economic%20uncertainty%2C%20more%20travelers%20opt%20for%20her%20firm's%20minimum%20budget%20bookings%20rather%20than%20their%20more%20expensive%20offerings.%20She%20said%20that%20during%20last%20November's%20election%20season%2C%20minimum-cost%20bookings%20surged%3B%20that%20happened%20yet%20again%20in%20April%20and%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnecdotally%2C%20our%20team%20mentioned%20that%20we've%20had%20a%20few%20trips%20cancelled%20due%20to%20layoffs%20or%20fear%20of%20layoffs%2C%20but%20not%20a%20statistically%20significant%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20Rafson%20said.%20%26quot%3BOverall%2C%20I%20think%20people%20are%20quietly%20opting%20for%20a%20lower-budget%20road%20trip%20instead%20of%20a%20major%20summer%20trip.%20But%20they're%20still%20traveling!%20Just%20slightly%20differently.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224d2035cd-b0c3-4390-a94c-efd1129d645a%5C%22%3ESaying%20no%20to%20flying%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%2C%20flying%20might%20not%20be%20worth%20it%20right%20now%2C%20given%20recent%20stories%20of%20safety%20and%20timing%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20I%20live%20very%20close%20to%20Newark%20Airport%2C%20and%20the%20craziest%20delays%20are%20happening%20with%20the%20air%20traffic%20control%20and%20stuff%20%E2%80%94%20I%20mean%2C%20that%20alone%20is%20making%20people%20iffy%20about%20traveling%2C%26quot%3B%20Dan%20Pieraccini%2C%20an%20avid%20domestic%20traveler%20and%20road%20tripper%20based%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20travelers%20are%20opting%20for%20road%20trips%20just%20because%20they%20want%20to%3B%20Scott%20Reing%2C%2037%2C%20is%20planning%20a%202%2C500-mile-long%20road%20trip%20for%20his%20family%20to%20the%20Grand%20Canyon%20to%20commemorate%20his%20wedding%20anniversary.%20His%20family%20alternates%20between%20bigger%20vacations%20abroad%20and%20domestic%20trips%20to%20national%20parks.%20This%20year%20happened%20to%20be%20a%20national%20parks%20year.%20In%20theory%2C%20he%20said%2C%20some%20of%20the%20appeal%20of%20the%20domestic%20trip%20this%20time%20around%20is%20price%2C%20although%20the%20cost%20will%20still%20be%20hefty%20with%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20they're%20spending%20on%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20kind%20of%20have%20more%20control%20over%20what%20you're%20spending%20when%20you're%20doing%20a%20road%20trip%20versus%20going%20to%20an%20all-inclusive%20or%20going%20on%20a%20cruise%20or%20flying%20abroad%2C%26quot%3B%20Reing%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20really%20have%20the%20choice%20to%20stay%20in%20a%20motel%20or%20a%20campsite%20one%20night%20or%20two%20nights%20or%2010%20nights%20versus%20something%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20Reing%20said%20he%20isn't%20broadly%20rethinking%20travel%20or%20travel%20spending%3B%20next%20year%2C%20he%20could%20end%20up%20somewhere%20abroad%2C%20like%20Japan.%20Indeed%2C%20many%20Americans%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feurope-summer-travel-americans-economic-uncertainty-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estill%20opting%20for%20European%20or%20international%20travel%20this%20summer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20some%20powering%20through%20uncertainties%20and%20deciding%20it's%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20road%20is%20still%20calling.%20Cathy%20Keibler%2C%20a%2065-year-old%20retiree%20in%20Indiana%2C%20is%20eagerly%20planning%20her%20first%20major%20road%20trip%20across%20the%20country.%20She%20wants%20to%20see%20the%20country%2C%20but%20has%20no%20desire%20to%20fly%20anymore.%20She%20and%20her%20husband%20have%20a%20new%20Prius%2C%20so%20they're%20not%20too%20concerned%20about%20gas%20expenses%20and%20are%20planning%20to%20bring%20a%20cooler%20to%20mitigate%20food%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeibler%20also%20wants%20to%20get%20a%20closer%20view%20of%20what's%20happening%20in%20her%20own%20country%3B%20with%20unrest%20and%20uncertainty%2C%20a%20road%20trip%20offers%20an%20opportunity%20to%20see%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efirsthand%20how%20that's%20reflected%20in%20different%20corners%20of%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPart%20of%20the%20more%20idealistic%20reason%20for%20making%20this%20road%20trip%20is%20to%20maybe%20try%20to%20get%20in%20touch%20a%20little%20bit%20with%20really%20what's%20happening%20out%20there%20in%20the%20country%20in%20a%20way%20that%20we%20can't%20really%20do%20when%20we're%20just%20driving%20on%20the%20interstates%20and%20maybe%20pulling%20over%20at%20a%20McDonald's%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20going%20on%20a%20road%20trip%2C%20or%20cutting%20travel%20costs%20in%20other%20ways%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailt